02:11:06.183 --> 02:11:09.733
Visual on Coughlin,
heading south toward Boylston.

02:11:09.895 --> 02:11:11.772
Hotel parking lot on Van Ness.

02:11:11.939 --> 02:11:13.737
He's dressed as B.P.D.

02:11:14.191 --> 02:11:15.317
<i>Copy.</i>

02:11:15.484 --> 02:11:17.031
Officer.

02:11:18.904 --> 02:11:20.406
Coughlin.

02:11:59.195 --> 02:12:00.868
Drop your weapon!

02:12:02.698 --> 02:12:04.291
No!

02:12:06.369 --> 02:12:08.042
Move! Move!

02:12:32.812 --> 02:12:35.361
Coughlin, throw down your weapon.

02:12:37.608 --> 02:12:39.406
Fuck you.

02:12:39.902 --> 02:12:41.495
Let me see those hands, right now.

02:12:41.654 --> 02:12:43.247
Fuck you!

02:12:50.621 --> 02:12:52.339
Move, move.

02:12:53.541 --> 02:12:55.259
You got 30 seconds, asshole.

02:13:23.988 --> 02:13:25.365
Okay.

02:13:25.531 --> 02:13:27.283
I surrender.

02:13:27.575 --> 02:13:29.043
I surrender.

02:14:30.763 --> 02:14:33.391
Rusty, something went wrong.

02:14:33.557 --> 02:14:34.729
Come here.

02:14:45.861 --> 02:14:47.238
Fergie.

02:14:48.280 --> 02:14:49.281
Prick.

02:15:20.354 --> 02:15:21.947
Fergie...

02:15:22.648 --> 02:15:24.992
remember who clipped your nuts for you.

02:15:26.318 --> 02:15:30.323
<i>I came in hot, saw the suspect run
across the street with a Tec-9.</i>

02:15:30.489 --> 02:15:35.165
I lit up the tires, I jumped out of the cruiser,
engaged the suspect in gunfire.

02:15:36.203 --> 02:15:37.204
So that's when...

02:15:37.371 --> 02:15:39.169
- you get out of your cruiser.
- Yeah.

02:15:39.331 --> 02:15:42.926
At that point, I fired, struck the suspect
at least once or twice.

02:15:43.085 --> 02:15:44.211
Hey.

02:15:44.503 --> 02:15:46.096
<i>Multiple victims down.</i>

02:15:46.255 --> 02:15:48.053
<i>Location, 529 Main Street, Charlestown.</i>

02:15:48.215 --> 02:15:50.684
- <i>Uniformed officers on the scene.</i>
- That's the Florist.

02:15:50.843 --> 02:15:52.390
Hey, Bobby, Bobby, what happened?

02:15:52.553 --> 02:15:54.180
Somebody got Fergie.

02:15:55.889 --> 02:15:57.937
- Jesus Christ, that's gotta be MacRay.
- Fuck.

02:16:04.815 --> 02:16:07.193
<i>Claire, it's me.</i>

02:16:07.484 --> 02:16:08.531
<i>Are you okay?</i>

02:16:09.528 --> 02:16:10.529
<i>I'll be fine. I know.</i>

02:16:10.696 --> 02:16:13.165
<i>But I'm okay. I'm all right.</i>

02:16:13.324 --> 02:16:15.076
<i>Claire, I wanna meet you.</i>

02:16:16.702 --> 02:16:20.047
<i>It's gotta be soon.
I don't have a lot of time.</i>

02:16:21.540 --> 02:16:23.042
<i>Can you meet me?</i>

02:16:24.043 --> 02:16:25.215
<i>Claire, please.</i>

02:16:26.045 --> 02:16:28.468
<i>I need to know. I gotta go.</i>

02:16:29.506 --> 02:16:31.224
Can you come here?

02:16:37.222 --> 02:16:39.270
You want me to come 
where you are now?

02:16:39.600 --> 02:16:40.816
<i>Mm-hm.</i>

02:16:44.730 --> 02:16:47.233
I don't think
that's a good idea for me.

02:16:51.028 --> 02:16:52.245
Why?

02:16:57.575 --> 02:16:59.374
What if there are police there?

02:17:01.413 --> 02:17:03.005
<i>There's no one here.</i>

02:17:08.754 --> 02:17:11.678
All right, well, if you think I should
probably come by there...

02:17:11.840 --> 02:17:14.263
then I guess that's what I'll do. Yeah.

02:17:15.761 --> 02:17:16.933
Okay.

02:17:18.430 --> 02:17:21.228
<i>Claire, listen, I'm--
Listen. Listen to me.</i>

02:17:23.394 --> 02:17:24.896
<i>I'm sorry, okay?</i>

02:17:26.313 --> 02:17:28.531
I'm sorry for what I did to you.

02:17:29.941 --> 02:17:31.285
Remember that.

02:17:31.985 --> 02:17:34.955
<i>Come down in the back
and let me in in about an hour.</i>

02:17:37.782 --> 02:17:39.251
All right?

02:17:41.120 --> 02:17:42.746
I'll see you.

02:17:44.164 --> 02:17:45.962
Wait, Doug? Doug?

02:17:47.084 --> 02:17:48.552
- Yeah.
- <i>I want you to come.</i>

02:17:48.710 --> 02:17:51.635
<i>I really wanna see you.</i>

02:17:56.343 --> 02:17:59.313
It'll be just like one of my sunny days.

02:18:11.608 --> 02:18:12.825
Well...

02:18:14.986 --> 02:18:16.660
I'm on my way then.

02:18:19.491 --> 02:18:20.492
Bye.

02:18:24.163 --> 02:18:26.085
Goodbye, Claire.

02:18:32.212 --> 02:18:34.431
All right,
I'd say we've done our part here.

02:18:34.590 --> 02:18:37.218
You know what? Not now.

02:18:43.182 --> 02:18:46.026
<i>I know he says he's coming, 
but I want people at Logan, South Station...</i>

02:18:46.184 --> 02:18:48.563
downtown, Greyhound, subway, 
everything. Now.

02:18:48.728 --> 02:18:50.982
- <i>The city's covered.</i>
- <i>Good.</i>

02:19:13.754 --> 02:19:16.507
<i>We're secure, and everything's ready.</i>

02:19:22.763 --> 02:19:26.734
- Sir, we need you to stay off the street.
- Just going to work. No problem.

02:19:42.907 --> 02:19:44.660
- How long?
- Forty minutes.

02:19:45.160 --> 02:19:47.037
- Alleyway clear?
- Yes, sir.

02:20:00.551 --> 02:20:03.646
<i>We got nothing.
Still no movement in the alley. Over.</i>

02:20:05.013 --> 02:20:08.267
Well, I guess he didn't have as big 
a thing for you as you thought.

02:20:10.018 --> 02:20:11.861
I guess not.

02:20:33.667 --> 02:20:35.260
"My sunny days." 

02:20:42.843 --> 02:20:45.642
You know, Claire,
we are a national organization.

02:20:53.687 --> 02:20:56.782
All right, boys, let's pack it up.
He ain't coming.

02:20:56.940 --> 02:20:59.409
Let's get the description out.
Let's go.

02:20:59.651 --> 02:21:01.494
We know what he looks like.

02:21:02.529 --> 02:21:03.872
Let's go find him.

02:21:07.492 --> 02:21:08.618
All right. You good?

02:21:08.785 --> 02:21:10.583
Hey, best possible outcome, you know.

02:21:10.746 --> 02:21:12.669
Well done, well done.

02:21:50.452 --> 02:21:51.920
It's for you.

02:22:57.269 --> 02:23:00.694
<i>Claire, take this.</i>

02:23:00.981 --> 02:23:03.609
<i>You'll do better with it than I can.</i>

02:23:04.234 --> 02:23:06.828
<i>By the time you read this,
I'll be long gone.</i>

02:23:06.987 --> 02:23:08.284
<i>Not the way I planned it...</i>

02:23:08.780 --> 02:23:12.830
<i>but for the first time in my life,
I'm leaving this city.</i>

02:23:25.422 --> 02:23:26.469
<i>Maybe if I go...</i>

02:23:27.549 --> 02:23:29.176
<i>I can stop looking.</i>

02:23:51.198 --> 02:23:52.916
<i>No matter how much you change...</i>

02:23:53.075 --> 02:23:55.999
<i>You still have to pay the price
for the things you've done.</i>

02:23:59.164 --> 02:24:01.007
<i>So I got a long road.</i>

02:24:06.671 --> 02:24:09.015
<i>But I know I'll see you again.</i>

02:24:14.846 --> 02:24:16.848
<i>This side or the other.</i>

